Top 20 Amber Fragrances | Favorite Warm Spicy Amber Perfumes

My thoughts on 20 different Amber Fragrances, my favorite Warm, Spicy, Amber, Oriental Perfumes. Do you enjoy these Fragrances? What is your favorite out of the 20 here? And if your favorite is not mentioned what is it? Please let me know, add a comment below so that I can find out. 

HISTOIRES DE PARFUMS AMBRE 114: Amber, Vanilla, Benzoin, Tonka Beans, Sandalwood, Nutmeg, Patchouli, Musk
DIOR AMBRE NUIT: Rose, Amber
ORMONDE JAYNE TOLU: Tolu Balsam, Amber, Tonka Beans, Olibanum, Orchid, Rose, Lily-Of-The-Valley, Orange Blossom
TAUER PERFUMES LDDM: Amber, Labdanum, Coriander, Petitgrain, Cumin, Cedar, Vetiver, Patchouli, Birch, Geranium
TEO CABANEL BARKHANE: Myrrh, Labdanum, Tonka Beans, Vanilla, Curry Tree, Patchouli, Oud, Cumin
CARNER BARCELONA AMBAR DEL SUR: Amber, Myrrh, Vanilla, Tonka Beans, Labdanum, Patchouli, Sandalwood, Jasmine
ISABEY AMBRE DE CARTHAGE: Amber Labdanum, Osmanthus, Sandalwood, Patchouli, Olibanum, Musk, Tea, Jasmine
ACQUA DI PARMA AMBRA: Ambergris, Musk, Marine Notes
I PROFUMI DI FIRENZE AMBRA DEL NEPAL: Vanilla, Ambergris, Sandalwood, Incense, Musk, Oakmoss, Patchouli
GALLIVANT ISTANBUL: Amber, Opoponax, Cardamom, Tonka Beans, Vanilla, Sandalwood, Musk, 
FRANCESCA BIANCHI SEX AND THE SEA: Ambergris, Pineapple, Coconut, Mimosa, Iris, Immortelle, Civet, Vanilla, Benzoin, Myrrh
ROJA PARFUMS AMBER AOUD: Oud, Ambergris, Rose, Saffron, Fig, Civet, Birch, Cinnamom, Orris, Musk, Sandalwood
YSL CAFTAN: Benzoin, Labdanum, Olibanu, Styrax, Musk, Pink Pepper, Tangerine, Bergamot
PARFUM D'EMPIRE AMBRE RUSSE: Amber, Incense, Leather, Cinnamon, Vodka, Champagne, Tea, Coriander, Birh
JOVOY AMBRE PREMIER: Amber, Patchouli, Vanilla, Spices, Rose, Citruses
ALGHABRA PARFUMS KING OF FLOWERS: Amber, Sandalwood, Iris, Lavender, Bergamot, Grapefruit 
RANIA J AMBRE LOUP: Labdanum, Guaiac Wood, Vanilla, Peru Balsam
MAITRE PARFUMEUR ET GANTIER AMBRE PRECIEUX ULTIME: Amber, Vanilla, Lavender, Vanilla, Tolu Balsam, Labdanum
SERGE LUTENS AMBRE SULTAN: Resins, Amber, Bay, Myrrh, Sandalwood, Benzoin, Coriander, Vanilla, Oregano
MAISON FRANCIS KURKDJIAN GRAND SOIR: Amber, Benzoin, Vanilla, Tonka Beans, Labdanum
